									<h2>

							Pedestrian Cases are Different
					</h2>

									<p>Every pedestrian accident has its own facts: the time of day, lighting, traffic signals, driver behavior, speed, visibility, and pedestrian actions all matter. AccidentLogic takes those details into account when identifying which lawyer is best suited to handle a case.</p><p>By focusing on attorneys who regularly represent injured pedestrians and their families, AccidentLogic gives users a better chance of working with counsel who already understands the patterns, defenses, and evidence that shape these claims.</p>

